StorySetUp_key1: name: Story Setup or Git Setup
StorySetUp_key2: Aap ek nayi Project directory **Stories** banaiye
StorySetUp_key3: Apne Stories directory mein navigate kijiye
StorySetUp_key4: Stories directory mein navigate karne ke baad aap **git init** command run kijiye
StorySetUp_key5: Iss command ke baad **git** humare iss directory mein banaye hue content ko track karna shuru kar dega.
StorySetUp_key7: Git ke documentation mein ja kar **git init** command ke baare mein padhe
